Package fi.group4.project.entity

Class SimulationRun

java.lang.Object
fi.group4.project.entity.SimulationRun
@Entity public class SimulationRun extends Object
Represents a simulation run with specific parameters, a random seed, timestamp, and distribution type.

    • SimulationRun

      public SimulationRun(int param1, int param2, int param3, int param4, int param5, long seed, long ts, String distribution)
      Constructs a SimulationRun with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      param1 - the number of planners involved in the simulation
      param2 - the number of implementers involved in the simulation
      param3 - the number of reviewers involved in the simulation
      param4 - the number of testers involved in the simulation
      param5 - the number of deployers involved in the simulation
      seed - the random seed used for simulation reproducibility
      ts - the timestamp when the simulation run was created
      distribution - the type of distribution used in the simulation (e.g., normal, uniform)
